msgid ""
"The IOU badge count on the top-nav **IOU** tab is populated by "
"`IouZakenSection` via an `onCountChange` callback — identical pattern to the "
"task count badge on the **Projecten** tab."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:90
msgid ""
"`IouZakenSection` is shared by both list views; the `WORK_ITEM_FIELDS` "
"constant controls which markdown sections are extracted and displayed per "
"card. Main content area overflow corrected from `flex-col` to `block` so all "
"long-form sections scroll correctly."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:92
msgid ""
"To enable the IOU tab for another tenant, add an `iou` key with the four "
"section entries to that tenant's `leftPanelSections` in `tenants.json`. No "
"code changes are required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:94
msgid "Backend — IOU public endpoints"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:96
msgid ""
"`GET /v1/public/use-cases` added to `public.routes.ts`. Lists GitLab issues "
"for `GITLAB_PROJECT_PATH`; supports `?state=opened` (default) or "
"`?state=closed`; returns up to 100 items sorted by `created_at` descending. "
"Returns `iid`, `title`, `state`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `web_url`, "
"`labels`, `assignees`, and `description` per item. No authentication "
"required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:98
msgid ""
"`POST /v1/public/feedback` added to `public.routes.ts`. Accepts `multipart/"
"form-data` with fields `name`, `org`, `role`, `contact`, `description`, and "
"up to 5 image files under the field name `screenshots`. Each image is first "
"uploaded to the GitLab project uploads API; the returned markdown references "
"are embedded in the issue body. Uses `multer` in-memory storage with a per-"
"file 10 MB limit and an image-only `fileFilter`. No authentication required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:100
msgid ""
"Both endpoints require `GITLAB_TOKEN`, `GITLAB_BASE_URL`, and "
"`GITLAB_PROJECT_PATH` to be set. Missing configuration returns `503 "
"GITLAB_NOT_CONFIGURED`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:102
msgid ""
"See [IOU GitLab Integration]{1} for full setup instructions, environment "
"variable reference, and the curl verification steps."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:106
msgid "v2.9.4 — Feature Release (March 30, 2026)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:108
msgid "AI Assistant — Multi-Source MCP Registry"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:110
msgid ""
"`McpClientService` singleton replaced by `McpRegistry` — a provider registry "
"that manages multiple independent MCP sources. Each provider connects, "
"exposes a curated set of tools, and contributes a section to the composite "
"system prompt independently. A provider failure does not block other "
"providers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:112
msgid ""
"`McpProvider` interface introduced: `id`, `displayName`, `description`, "
"`connect()`, `disconnect()`, `getToolDefinitions()`, `callTool()`, "
"`isConnected()`, `systemPromptContribution()`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:114
msgid ""
"`OperatonMcpProvider` replaces `McpClientService` — identical stdio "
"subprocess behaviour, 15-tool `ALLOWED_TOOLS` curation gate preserved."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:116
msgid ""
"`TriplyDbMcpProvider` added — spawns the bundled `triplydb-mcp` stdio "
"server; connects to the RONL SPARQL endpoint (`stevengort/RONL`). Exposes 11 "
"tools: `dmn_list`, `dmn_get`, `dmn_chain_links`, `dmn_enhanced_chain_links`, "
"`dmn_semantic_equivalences`, `organization_list`, `service_list`, "
"`rule_list`, `concept_list`, `service_rules_metadata`, `sparql_query`. "
"Enabled via `TRIPLYDB_MCP_ENABLED=true`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:118
msgid ""
"`McpRegistry.getToolDefinitions(providerIds?)` and `callTool()` accept an "
"optional provider ID filter. `buildSystemPrompt(providerIds?)` assembles a "
"composite prompt from only the selected connected providers. `getProviderMeta"
"()` returns metadata and connection status for all registered providers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:120
msgid ""
"`POST /v1/mcp/chat` extended with `sources: string[]` — provider IDs "
"selected by the user for the session. `GET /v1/mcp/sources` added — returns "
"provider metadata and connection status."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:122
msgid ""
"Frontend: source selector toggle buttons rendered below the message history. "
"All connected sources pre-selected by default; offline providers shown "
"greyed-out. Send button and textarea disabled when no sources are selected. "
"Header subtitle shows active source display names dynamically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:124
msgid ""
"Markdown rendering added to assistant bubbles via `react-markdown` + "
"`@tailwindcss/typography` prose classes. In-progress streaming bubble also "
"renders Markdown incrementally."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:128
msgid "v2.9.3 — Feature Release (March 26, 2026)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:130
msgid "Caseworker Dashboard — Berichten & Regelcatalogus"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:132
msgid ""
"Berichten endpoint switched from hardcoded seed data to the Provincie "
"Flevoland RSS feed (`flevoland.nl/Content/Pages/Loket?rss=news`) — same "
"axios/regex pattern as the Nieuws service, 10-minute cache TTL."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:133
msgid ""
"HTML entities decoded server-side (`nbsp`, `amp`, `euro`, `lt`, `gt`, `quot`)"
"; action link populated from RSS `<link>` element as \"Lees meer\"."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:134
msgid ""
"`getBerichtById()` now reads from the live cache instead of the removed "
